{"tid":2307364,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"武肺係一個清理廢佬嘅一個天賜良機 根本就冇嘢可怕","createTime":"2020-12-01T06:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T07:33:13.000Z","uid":156109,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d557047757ec1565b68393120aab534ba66f5c06","tid":2307364,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:36:15.000Z","msg":"事先聲明<br />\n唔好誤會 我唔係針對老年人<br />\n只要你係有腦嘅 即使上咗年紀<br />\n平時小心啲嘅話根本唔會有咩事 <br />\n<br />\n對於一般年輕人黎講 不外乎都只係一個flu <br />\n醫返好就冇事 死亡率極低 <br />\n<br />\n對於廢老黎講就唔同 明顯易死好多<br />\n去得跳舞群組 搞到大爆發嘅都係啲冇腦嘅廢老黎<br />\n到頭來埋單 要死嘅都係死佢哋 <br />\n<br />\n一個病毒做到嘅攬炒同對政權嘅衝擊 <br />\n比起抗爭者冒住生命危險做到嘅大百倍千倍 <br />\n我哋要做嘅就係做好自己 保護好自己先<br />\n睇住班人頭豬腦嘅廢老點樣將個疫情延續落去<br />\n搞到百業蕭條 清返咁上下無用嘅人口<br />\n成個社會到時可能會比依家更加清新"},{"pid":"47b8d75b04cc245f9dfef6b1ff27c91476d04be5","tid":2307364,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cdfa94cc0c19ca1e57e07414b9e7fd9576ed5a","tid":2307364,"uid":2889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:38:51.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"a5d2b4dc31bfbf7076a47ec6380eedde419d76e2","tid":2307364,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485dd820936a420bf0b257b8b2e4dff0b09aa594","tid":2307364,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae44b6bfed3d9b1e9b0eaab23a04037cc77cab4","tid":2307364,"uid":156109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:41:58.000Z","msg":"見到疫情爆到去第4波 政府唔肯封關<br />\n根本就唔洗感到憤怒 無力<br />\n我哋應該擁抱呢場疫情 由佢哋自己死咁啲仲好"},{"pid":"0ce4d24178bc329dcbdca14946edd5d0b5119c4d","tid":2307364,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020